results.name: Number of states in the n-th shell of the nuclear shell model.
comment: Partial sums of the first seven terms give the "magic numbers" A018226.
Also the partial sums of the first eight terms give the positive first eight terms of A162626 (and possibly more).
reference: M. Goeppert Mayer and J. Hans D. Jensen, Elementary Theory of Nuclear Shell Structure, J. Wiley and Sons, Inc. (1955).
I. Talmi, Simple Models of Complex Nuclei, Hardwood Academic Publishers (1993).
results.author: _Omar E. Pol_, Jun 04 2012
